      <description>&lt;main class="wp-block-group is-layout-flow wp-block-group-is-layout-flow"&gt; &lt;div class="wp-block-group is-layout-constrained wp-block-group-is-layout-constrained"&gt;&lt;h1 class="wp-block-post-title"&gt;KnH Characters *&lt;/h1&gt;   &lt;div style="height:1px" aria-hidden="true" class="wp-block-spacer"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;   &lt;/div&gt;   &lt;div class="entry-content wp-block-post-content is-layout-constrained wp-block-post-content-is-layout-constrained"&gt; &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;WIP. Let me know if I make any mistakes.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" /&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-center"&gt;ALPHABETICAL ORDER; OPEN SPOILERS&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-center"&gt;No longer up to date with translations.&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-center"&gt;use ctrl-F to navigate&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" /&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-center"&gt;NAMED CLANS&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Ka (Imperial Clan)&lt;br&gt;Known living members: The emperor, Jinshi, Rinrii, two male infants&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Rat&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;#8211; Shi (Former Regents of the Northern Province)&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Fallen as of the end of Arc 3&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;Known members: Shishou, Shenmei, Rouran, Suirei, Chou&amp;#8217;u, Surviving Shi clan children&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Rabbit&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;#8211; U (Declining Clan)&lt;br&gt;Known members: Uryuu, Riishu, Yakou, Ujun&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Snake&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;#8211; Mi (Imperial Spies)&lt;br&gt;Known members: Chue, Yao&amp;#8217;s uncle, Gyoku&amp;#8217;ou&amp;#8217;s wife, Fuuran&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Horse&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;#8211; Ma (Imperial Guards)&lt;br&gt;Known members: Gaoshun, Basen, Maamei, Baryou, Taomei, Bakin&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dog&lt;/strong&gt; &amp;#8211; I (Former Regents of the Western Province)&amp;nbsp;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Fallen during the reign of the Empress Regnant&lt;br&gt;&lt;/em&gt;Known former members: Rikuson&lt;em&gt;, &lt;/em&gt;Haku&amp;#8217;u, Seki&amp;#8217;u, Koku&amp;#8217;u&lt;em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Wind-reader tribe &lt;br&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Male members split from the clan after reaching the age of majority&lt;br&gt;&lt;/em&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; Known: Gyoku&amp;#8217;en&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Ra (Clan of Eccentrics)&lt;br&gt;Known members: Rakan, Rahan, Rakou, Junjie, Rahan&amp;#8217;s mother, Rahan&amp;#8217;s grandfather, Luomen, Maomao&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;You (Current Regents of the Western Province)&lt;br&gt;Known Members: Gyoku&amp;#8217;en, Gyoku&amp;#8217;ou, Gyokuyou, Gyokujun, Shikyou, Daahai, Inshin, Fuuran, Feilon   &lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Dragon &lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#8211; Shin (Former imperials)&lt;br&gt;Known Members: Yuu&amp;#8217;en, Shin clan matriarch and her advisor&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ox &lt;/strong&gt;&amp;#8211; Chuu (Organisers of the Named Clan Meeting)&lt;br&gt;Known Members: Chuuki&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;hr class="wp-block-separator has-alpha-channel-opacity" /&gt;    &lt;p class="has-text-align-center"&gt;CHARACTERS&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Aaduo (Ah Duo)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Pure Consort &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Popular with court ladies in the inner palace&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Gallant and handsome&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Stepped down at the end of ARC1 &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Pridefully as if she fulfilled the consort&amp;#8217;s duty&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Current Emperor&amp;#8217;s consort from the time he was the Crown Prince &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;had a son with him &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;who passed away for reasons unknown &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;accidentally poisoned by her head maid Fonmin with honey&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;is the baby her real son, or swapped with the real imperial brother? &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(LN5)&lt;span style="text-decoration: underline"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Knows Jinshi is her son Yue. Decided to just watch over him, doesn&amp;#8217;t care who he picks as his consort. Aww&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN5) Swapped her son with the real imperial brother on purpose. Anshi was eager to do it (she seemed to hate her own son)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;lost her uterus in the process&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Current Emperor&amp;#8217;s milk-sibling (i.e. shared the same nursing mother) &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;one year older than him&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Close friends&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Loves to drink&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC4) Her father wasn&amp;#8217;t anyone important&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC4) Intelligent, but in return for that, her emotional intelligence is a little lacking&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Close with Riishu, whom she treated somewhat like a daughter&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Lived in Garnet Palace &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(End of ARC1) Moved to Southern Imperial Villa&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Jinshi looks very similar to her &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(ARC3) Working as Jinshi&amp;#8217;s body double &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;dresses up as a man&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN5) &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;the emperor made a promise to her when they were younger&lt;/span&gt; &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;that he will make her his empress&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;she wonders how that will turn out in the long run&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Aira&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(LN4) &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Western lady (Gyokuyou&amp;#8217;s race) who seems to be in cahoots with Shenmei?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Airin&amp;#8217;s political rival&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Former Sha&amp;#8217;ou priestess&amp;#8217; candidate&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Airan (Ailan)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Noble Consort Gyokuyou&amp;#8217;s maid&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Tall&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Baryou (Maliang)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC7&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Gaoshun&amp;#8217;s eldest son, and second child&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Social anxiety &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;can only deal with familiar people&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Brain smart, but physically weak&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Married to Chue, a woman who descended from the Mi Clan &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;has a son with her&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;who is the best at dealing with him&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(Arc 8) Joined the expedition to the Western Capital&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Basen (Mashan)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Member of the Ma Clan &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Gaoshun&amp;#8217;s youngest son&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Has an older brother and an older sister&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Taking over his father as Jinshi&amp;#8217;s aide&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Unsociable and short-tempered, but conscientious at his work&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Extremely sturdy &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;survived from getting trampled on a horse (Start of Arc5)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Extremely strong&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Nervous habit of raising his right shoulder when working as his father&amp;#8217;s substitute&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Can&amp;#8217;t deal with women, especially those who use their gender as a weapon &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt; his mother and his sister made him that way&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;fine with Maomao though&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC4) Crushing hard on Riishu&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC8) Joined the expedition to the Western Capital&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Chue (Que)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Arc 8&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Descended from the Mi Clan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Baryou&amp;#8217;s wife &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;has a son with him&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;under pressure to make another child from her mother-in-law&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Idiosyncratic personality &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;knows magic tricks&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Joined the expedition to the Western Capital &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;as one of Jinshi&amp;#8217;s attendants&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;accompanies Maomao a lot (body guard?)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC9) A competent spy &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Boss is not Jinshi&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Worked together with Rin-shoujin to get their hands on the family register&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Chou&amp;#8217;u (Zhaoyu)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Member of the Shi Clan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Living in the pleasure district with Maomao&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Plays with the kamuro and the manservant&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Front teeth missing &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;looks goofy&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Missing his past memories and the left side of his body is numb from the drug&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Good at drawing &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(ARC6) Getting taught by an up and coming artist&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Doesn&amp;#8217;t seem to be interested in medicine (much to Maomao&amp;#8217;s disappointment)&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN4) Old name was Kyou&amp;#8217;u&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN4) Son of Shirou&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN4) Was close with Maomao when she was abducted in the Shi Clan fortress&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Court Physician Ri (Li)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;High ranking court physician&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC 8) Joined the expedition to the western capital &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(ARC9) The only normal court physician&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Court Physician Ryuu (Liu)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;High ranking court physician&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;In charge of all the court physicians in the imperial court&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Old colleague of Ruomen&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Strict&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Court Physician You (Yang)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;High ranking court physician&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(Arc 8) Joined the expedition to the western capital &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;In charge of the selected group of court physicians&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Tanned &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Looks like a local of the western capital&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC9) is a local, from the old You family&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Hardworking and genuine &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Bashful about showing himself off&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Flexible thinking&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Not interested in politics&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Daahai (Dahai)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Gyoku&amp;#8217;en&amp;#8217;s third son&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Oversees the ports of Isei Province&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Emperor (Current)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;In his prime; 30s&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Has three surviving children &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Rinrii&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(END of ARC3) Current Crown Prince by Gyokuyou&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(END of ARC3) Another son by Rifa&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Has four dead children &amp;gt; two princes and two princesses&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Has a great beard&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Benevolent and wise ruler&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC7) Loss against Jinshi on a Go game with a bet, which allowed the latter to request to become a &amp;#8220;eunuch&amp;#8221; and get out of being the crown prince &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;doesn&amp;#8217;t regret it, since he got a happy marriage and children out of it&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Calls Jinshi &amp;#8220;Yue&amp;#8221;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Emperor (Previous)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Foolish ruler &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;dim-witted&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;ruled as his mother&amp;#8217;s puppet&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN3) Older brothers all died from a disease, as they were inbred. Only he was spared as his mother was a maidservant rather than a noble&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Looks like a celestial maiden when he was younger &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;no shadow of it left in his final years&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Paedophile &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;terrified of adult women due to his overbearing mother&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;can only talk properly to young girls&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Has three children &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Banished Princess (See Suirei&amp;#8217;s mother),&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Current Emperor,&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Imperial Brother (See Jinshi)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Became a shut-in in his later years&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Quickly followed his mother to death shortly after she dies&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Deceased &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(LN)&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;from sulfur poisoning&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Empress (Empress Regnant)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;The Previous Emperor&amp;#8217;s Mother &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(LN3)&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;her only son&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Ruled with her son as the puppet ruler&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Terrifying, unable to be defied&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Worked with Shishou on curtailing the slave trade by expanding the inner palace &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;her legacy allowed the current emperor to abolish the slave trade&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN3)&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Started out as a maidservant &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Deceased&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Empress Dowager&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Current Emperor&amp;#8217;s mother&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN3) Name is Anshi &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;The illegitimate daughter of some noble&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Entered the inner palace as a middle-ranked consort&amp;#8217;s (as her older-half sister&amp;#8217;s) maid &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;older sister eventually got bestowed, left the inner palace&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;she was ten years old when they first met&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Got the previous emperor&amp;#8217;s attention by asking if he was fine &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;he was crying when her older sister touched his right arm&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;he eventually got scared of Anshi too when she grew up&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Middle-aged&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Also the mother of the Imperial Brother &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Is he really her son? Is this boy the son of the Previous Emperor?&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN5) Hated her own son, but cherished her grandson&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;En&amp;#8217;en (Yanyan)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC6&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;A court lady &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;court physician assistant&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Subordinate relationship with Yao&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Quiet&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Cunning&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Capable, but sabotaged her marks in the exam for Yao &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Knows a smattering of western language&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Knows medicines for beautification and gynaecological issues&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Yuri&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Not interested in becoming a court physician&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Feiron (Feilong)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC10&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Gyoku&amp;#8217;ou&amp;#8217;s second son&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Twenty-three years old&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Learning politics under Rikuson&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Tall, lanky&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Fenshen (Fengxian)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Top Class Courtesan of the Rokushoukan &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;reduced to a streetwalker after giving birth to Maomao&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;went deranged&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Maomao&amp;#8217;s mother&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Unsociable and haughty&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Good at Go&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Three Princesses&amp;#8217; Elder Sister&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN2) Alive, redeemed by Rakan, LN only&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN6) Married Rakan, LN only&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Deceased &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(LN6) Complications from syphilis &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;FonMin (Fengming)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Ah Duo&amp;#8217;s head maid&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;From a family of beekeepers &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;her family was also involved with the bride-nappings&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Accidentally killed Ah Duo&amp;#8217;s baby with honey&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Fanatically loyal to Ah Duo&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Hated Riishu who was close to her master &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;tried to kill Riishu many times since the girl knew about the poisonous honey&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(End of ARC1) Executed &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;hanging&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Former Court Physician&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Banished from the Inner Palace&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Outstanding physical &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Second only to Ruomen (according to Maomao)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Raised the Banished Princess, and Suirei&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Confined in his room by Shenmei to make the Elixer of Life for her &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;succeeded in creating resurrection drug&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Passed away five years ago from the events of ARC3 &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(ARC4)&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt; &lt;/span&gt;Still alive &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;tried a prototype version of the resurrection drug &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;successful, but woke up with amnesia&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;one of the old men with dementia in the old hot spring villa where the Shi Clan children were treated at the end of ARC3 &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Fuuran (Hulang)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC 10&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Gyoku&amp;#8217;ou&amp;#8217;s third son&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Eighteen years old&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Learning politics under Jinshi&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Personality is nothing like his name (cruel and greedy)&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Short, kind&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Fuyou (Furong)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Middle ranked consort&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Third Princess of a vassal nation&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN1) Delicate maiden who shuts herself in her room and is laughed at by the other consorts&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Talented in dancing &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;but didn&amp;#8217;t display it to the emperor in hopes of taking his interest off her&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Danced on the Inner Palace Wall &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;started a ghost story panic in the Inner Palace&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;as a prayer for her childhood friend&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Bestowed to childhood friend as an award for feat of arms &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Happy ending&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC 8) Back home in Anan, happily married and pregnant&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Gaoshun (Gaoshun)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Jinshi&amp;#8217;s aide &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(ARC4) his son Basen takes over&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Member of the Ma Clan (clan head?)&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Looks like a military officer, but is a eunuch? &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Pretty high ranking military officer&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC7) Works as the emperor&amp;#8217;s aid&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;World-wisely man&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;talented in both the pen and the sword&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;The wrinkles on his forehead at getting deeper&amp;#8230;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Henpecked husband &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Married to Taomei&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Has two sons, one daughter &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;In order of age: Maamei, Baryou, Basen&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Has three grandchildren&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Grandmaster of Go (Kisei)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Emperor&amp;#8217;s Go instructor&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Only person who can defeat Rakan in Go &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Likens Rakan to a beast&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;He plays dirty to ensure best possible chance of victory &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;by serving salty dim sum&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Elderly man&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Smart and crafty&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Guien (Guiyuan)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Gyokuyou&amp;#8217;s maid&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Calm personality&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Gyoku&amp;#8217;en (Yuyuan)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Gyokuyou&amp;#8217;s father&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Governor of the western capital&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN5) Hosted the banquet at Seii Province&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC7) Currently in the capital &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;for a ceremony to become Named&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC9 end) Former member of the Ih clan, become to wind&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC9 end) All of his children are adopted &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Sterile?&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC9 end) Working with Rikuson for the sake of the Western Capital&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Gyokujun (Yusun)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC 10&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Gyoku&amp;#8217;ou&amp;#8217;s eldest son&amp;#8217;s son &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;first grandkid&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Bratty kid &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Hit the quack doctor&amp;#8217;s shin with a wooden sword&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;doesn&amp;#8217;t feel remorse over it&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Gyoku&amp;#8217;ou (Yuying)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Gyokuyou&amp;#8217;s older half brother &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;actually not related at all, adoptive half brother&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN8) Forties, same age range as Gyokuyou&amp;#8217;s mother &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Has children&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Looks like a typical Rii person&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC9) Rules over the farming villages of the western capital&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC9) Very popular in the western capital &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;called King Ou by some, a heroic character from a play&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Mother was a slave from Sha&amp;#8217;ou &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;a survivor of the plundered branch of the Wind-reader tribe&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Wants to wage war against Sha&amp;#8217;ou &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;all his machinations lead up to convincing the people of the Western Capital that Sha&amp;#8217;ou was the enemy&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Egotistical and self-righteous&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Freely lent money to farmers with crop failure &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;to tied them a contract to work for him during the event of an emergency &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;forcing farmers to &amp;#8220;conscription&amp;#8221;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(END of ARC9) Murdered by Rikuson&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Gyoku&amp;#8217;ou&amp;#8217;s eldest son (Shikyou)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC 10&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Deadbeat son &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;the one behind the lead-laced alcohol&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;the one who leaked the information for the bandits&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Completely excluded from the running to the new governer of the western capital despite birthright &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;never got the eduction to be a ruler&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Fights with Gyoku&amp;#8217;en&amp;#8217;s seventh son (second youngest) all the time&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Twenty-five years old&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Has one son &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;See, Gyokujun&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Plans drawn for his disinheritance&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Gyokuyou (Yuye)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Noble Consort &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(End of ARC3) Empress&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Twenty years old&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Has two children with the emperor &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Rinrii&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(End of ARC3) The Crown Prince &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(LN4) LN only, Breech birth &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;has his mother&amp;#8217;s red hair&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Red-haired and green-eyed&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Looks good in red&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Hailed from a trading post town at the edge of the empire &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(LN) Western Capital in Isei Province&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Daughter of Gyoku&amp;#8217;en&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN8) Daughter of a concubine, who is the same age as her older half-brother &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(ARC9) concubine was a former dancer, with red hair and blue eyes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN8) Bullied by her nieces and nephews as a child&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC3) Brought in three more maids to help out: Haku&amp;#8217;u, Seki&amp;#8217;u, Koku&amp;#8217;u. Sisters born a year after each other. &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;They knew each other from the Western Capital &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(ARC9) Her mother sheltered them as members of the former Ih clan with the sisters&amp;#8217; mother&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;The original three maids (Guien, Airan and Infa) treat these sisters with respect&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Honnyan (Hongniang)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Gyokuyou&amp;#8217;s head maid&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Extremely competent&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Already past the age to get married&amp;#8230; &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;&amp;#8220;A eunuch would be fine too at this point.&amp;#8221;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Imperial Brother&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Shut-in&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Wears a mask to hide his burn scars&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Doesn&amp;#8217;t work, useless&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Rumoured to be doted by the emperor and empress dowager, or shunned by the emperor&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;See Jinshi&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Back in public after ARC3&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Infa (Yinghua)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Gyokuyou&amp;#8217;s maid&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Lively personality&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Talkative&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Scared of lizards&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Likes ghost stories but terrified of them&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Irene (Airin)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Introduced in ARC4 &lt;span style="color: #333333"&gt;as a merchant&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;From Sha&amp;#8217;ou&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Tall, with sky coloured eyes &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;voluptuous figure&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;A priestess candidate &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;very close with the Sha&amp;#8217;ou Priestess&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Political enemies with Aira&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC4) Seeking asylum in Rii&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC6) Entered the Inner Palace alone as a middle-ranking consort &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;A scheme for the Sha&amp;#8217;ou Priestess to successfully &amp;#8220;die&amp;#8221; in another country without implicating Rii&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(END of ARC6) Now a criminal (a hostage in truth) in Rii &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;for &amp;#8220;poisoning&amp;#8221; the Sha&amp;#8217;ou Priestess&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Jinshi (Renshi)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Inner Palace Overseer &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Eunuch?&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;As a bet with the emperor &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;what is this bet?&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Throws away this identity at the end of ARC3 &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(ARC5) people close to him still call him Jinshi&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Ah Duo calls him Zui&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;other people refer to him as the Moon Prince/Prince of the Night &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;a hint to his real name ;D&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN5) the emperor calls him Yue&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Looks like a celestial maiden &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;wooed by both genders &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;much to his chagrin&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;he got his looks from the previous emperor &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;also looks like Ah Duo&amp;#8230;? &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(LN1) This poor dude got drunk the day before Ah Duo left the inner palace&amp;#8230;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Uses his appearance as a weapon&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Super clingy&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Naive young master&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Has a decently large frog (&lt;del&gt;I&amp;#8217;m sorry)&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Can tell apart truth and lies by looking at people&amp;#8217;s body language&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Seems to have more than one personality&amp;#8230; &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;sparkly eunuch mode&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;childish kid mode&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(End of ARC3) Stray dog mode &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;bolder, less androgynous &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;chemical castration drugs wearing off?&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Finds Maomao&amp;#8217;s reactions towards him refreshing&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Getting better at his interactions with Maomao &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;doing whatever he could to get her attention &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;just like an elementary school kid&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;reduced to a rare medicine supplier?&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Revealed to be Imperial Brother in ARC3 &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;birth secrets &amp;gt; crown prince?&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN3) Real name is Ka Zuigetsu&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN8) &lt;del&gt;A fucking masochist&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC8) Joined the expedition to the Western Capital&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Jazgul&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC6&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;A mute girl from Sha&amp;#8217;ou &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;part of the Sha&amp;#8217;ou priestess&amp;#8217; entourage&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Sold as a slave by her family due to famine&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Her drawings can depict future events&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;The next Sha&amp;#8217;ou Priestess&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Joka (Nühua)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Youngest of the Three Princesses of the Rokushoukan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Good at writing poetry&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Popular with officials&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Man-hater&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Mother was duped by the patron who fathered Joka &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;believed daughter is rightful of the Ka name (Imperial clan)&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;origin of Joka&amp;#8217;s hate of men?&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Named herself after the creation goddess&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC12/LN14) Father was a hunter who descended from an imperial &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Tianyu is her cousin&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Kanan (Henan)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Named in the LN only&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;One of Consort Riishu&amp;#8217;s maids &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;a food taster&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;switched her dish during the garden party as a prank&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Later upgraded to become Consort Riishu&amp;#8217;s headmaid &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;the consort&amp;#8217;s only ally&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Kokuyou (Keyong)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Introduced ARC5&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Maomao met him on the boat back to the capital after the banquet in Isei Province&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;A skilled rural doctor who got chased out of his village due to a fallout involving a witchdoctor &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;doesn&amp;#8217;t like witchdoctors&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;has smallpox scars &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;covers with a cloth&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;harmless but has a mischievous side to him&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;speaks of serious matters like gossipping aunties&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;finally finds work with an old acquaintance of Ruomen by the lake near the snake worshipping village&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC6) Hired by Maomao to manage the pharmacy and teach Sazen part-time&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Brought up by a westerner (further west than Sha&amp;#8217;ou) &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;who taught him medicine&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC12) and used him for medicine experimentation (twin trials)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Had a twin brother who died&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Kulumu&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC 9&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;A ten year old&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Self-proclaimed beautiful girl&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;The one behind the Hitouban case&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Lives in the western capital&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Child of a falconer&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Raised a barn owl herself with the intent of releasing it into the wild &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;her dad sold it to the Gyoku family as a gift to Gyoku&amp;#8217;ou&amp;#8217;s adoptive daughter&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;she came back to retrieve it&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Her family is close to the Gyoku family &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;educated by the Gyoku family&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Descendant of the Wind-reader tribe&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Smart child and very articulate for her age&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Madam&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Madam of the Rokushoukan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Miser&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Wants Maomao to become a courtesan &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;since this is the only life she knows&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;doesn&amp;#8217;t know/think prostitution is an occupation of misfortune&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Once a beautiful courtesan said to have tears of pearl&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Maamei (Mamei)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC7&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Gaoshun&amp;#8217;s eldest child, and only daughter &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;treated him like a caterpillar once&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Personality resembles her mother &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Strong-willed&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Happily married to a military official &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;a henpecked man&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Has two children&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Only person who can handle Baryou&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Maomao (Cat)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(LN3) Found in the inner palace by Rinrii &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;female calico&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;given an official title from the emperor &amp;#8220;Thief Investigator&amp;#8221;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;works in the quack doctor&amp;#8217;s office as the ratcatcher&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Introduced in arc 4 in the WN&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC4) The quack doctor wanted to take her back to his hometown&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC4) Somehow found her way back in a cart. Now lives in Rokushoukan, or is it Maomao&amp;#8217;s shack&amp;#8230;?&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN14) Now a proud mama&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Maomao (human)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Pharmacist of the Pleasure district&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Kidnapped to work in the Inner Palace &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(End of ARC1) later released and bought by Jinshi to work for him as a maid&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(End of ARC3) returns to the Pleasure district&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Obsessed with anything to do with poisons and drugs &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Using Jinshi to get her hands on more rare drugs of course&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Curious&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Mad scientist &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;left arm mutilated from self-experimentation&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN1) if she ever gets sentenced to death, she would want to go by poison&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Plain-faced, skinny, short &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;has freckles and spots drawn on her face&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Interested in childbirth but not childraising &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(End of ARC3) adopts Chou&amp;#8217;u&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Received kanzashi from: &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;one from Rihaku &amp;gt; cashed in to visit the Prostitution Quarter&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;one from Rifa&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;one from Jinshi &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(LN4) He keeps urging her to wear it, but she intended to sell it off someday&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN4) &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;she used it as a weapon and to skewer the snakes to grill them when she got imprisoned in a room with poisonous/venomous creatures&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN4)&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt; she gave it to Rouran as a promise to meet again after the uprising, who then consequently sold it at the end of the LN4 kek &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN5) &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;gets another one, which she mistakes it to be something Rahan had prepared for her with her outfit for the banquet&lt;/span&gt; &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;moon and poppy flower&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;she wore that one and Jinshi got possessive hmmm&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Bought up in the Rokushoukan &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Nursed by Pairin&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Raised by her adoptive father (great uncle), Ruomen, in the Pleasure district&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Father is Rakan &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;who completely dotes on her&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Mother is Fenshen&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC6) Back again in the imperial court as a court lady &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Court physician assistant&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(Arc 8) Learning the skills of a court physician (surgery)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC8) Joined the expedition to the Western Capital &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;to protect her from Rakan&amp;#8217;s public enemies back in the capital&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;to hammer in the quack doctor&amp;#8217;s role as Ruomen&amp;#8217;s body double&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;to manage Rakan if things go south?&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Meimei (Meimei)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Second oldest of the Three Princesses&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Short-tempered&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Black belly&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Good at Go and Shogi&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC5) Redeeming talks raised &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;A merchant&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Nenjen (Nianzhen)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Introduced in ARC9&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Elderly man from a farming village near the western capital &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Former serf&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Missing an eye and an index finger &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Eye from a person who tried to eat him out of starvation&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Finger as punishment for being a bandit&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Sentenced to do the Wind-Reader Tribe ritual for the rest of his life &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;works on the field, digging up dirt&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Only decent farmer in the village&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Former bandit &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;once skilled with the bow&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Part of the warmonger tribe that caused the locust plague 50 years ago &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;by massacring the Wind-Reader Tribe while they were in the middle of a ritual&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;only survivor of his tribe&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Onsou (Yincao)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC 9&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Rakan&amp;#8217;s new aide&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Worked with Rakan longer than Rikuson did&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Bows beautifully&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Pai, Lady (Bai-niangniang)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Introduced in ARC4&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Albino maiden&lt;/span&gt; &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;bad eyesight &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;sensitive ears, can hear high frequencies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Holds a show in the capital where she performs acts involving alchemy&lt;/span&gt; &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;drank mercury before the audience, which leads to a number of deaths in the capital&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;what is she trying to do?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;From a nomadic tribe?&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;(ARC5) somehow linked to the snake god worshipping village&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(END of ARC 5) Imprisoned in a villa away from the capital with Riishu&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC6) Hails from the same village as the Sha&amp;#8217;ou Priestess &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Supposed to be the next priestess&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;But got raised and taken away by someone who wished ill to the priestess (Aira?)&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC6) A hostage in Rii to control Sha&amp;#8217;ou&amp;#8217;s demands&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Pairin (Bailing)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Oldest of the Three Princesses &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;raised up the Rokushoukan when it was in decline&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Good at dancing&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Lust demon&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Maomao&amp;#8217;s nursing mother&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Paid off her own debt to the brothel already &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;only working because it matches her personality&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Dreams of being carried away by a prince on a white horse &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Rihaku is getting there&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Priestess&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC6&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Mentioned in ARC4 &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #333333"&gt;Age: thirties&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #333333"&gt;Menarche hasn&amp;#8217;t arrived yet&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Sha&amp;#8217;ou Priestess, one of the two pillars that govern the country&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Longest in power &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;a symbol of growing female power in the country&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;An albino castrato &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;used by the previous oracle as a means to take down the previous king&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;her true gender was kept from her until the previous oracle revealed it at her deathbed &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;went to recuperate in a remote village for a couple of years following that &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;where the xianbing artist found her and drew her&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Travels to Rii for medical treatment &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Men forbidden to touch her, so court ladies specialising in medicine were created as a new post for this&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Actually a ruse &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Looking for a means to die without letting the country know of her true gender&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Getting away from the schemes of the king&amp;#8217;s faction to marry her off&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Irene proposed the idea of dying on foreign soil so her body would be returned as bone shards&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(End of ARC6) &amp;#8220;Dies&amp;#8221; &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;now staying at Ah Duo&amp;#8217;s palace as an informant&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Quack Doctor (Gu&amp;#8217;en; Yuyuan)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;The sole imperial physician of the inner palace&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Boasts that he can make stomach pain medicine, but nothing else&amp;#8230;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Good person&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Always treat Maomao to tea and snacks whenever she comes to visit &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;depends on her to make medicine&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;loach moustache&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Son of paper makers &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;became a eunuch for money to support family due to failing paper trade&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Has an older sister who went into the inner palace, and a younger sister who is still in the papermaking village&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC 8) Joined the expedition to the Western Capital &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;as Ruomen&amp;#8217;s body double&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Rahan (Luoban)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Member of Ra Clan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Scion of Ra Clan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Rakan&amp;#8217;s adopted son and nephew &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;picked Rakan over his family&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC5) Still corresponds with his biological father, Rakou, through letters&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Maomao&amp;#8217;s cousin&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Miser&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Fox eyes &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Looks like a male version of Maomao with glasses&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Has various other businesses&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Specialty is numbers &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;obssessed with the golden ratio&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Can&amp;#8217;t drink&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC5) Gets seasick&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC6) Had a hand in getting Irene into the country as a middle-ranking consort&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC9) Sends a letter to Maomao, concealing a secret message that&amp;#8217;s revealed when read alongside Yao&amp;#8217;s letter, with the help of Rahan&amp;#8217;s older brother &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;stayed in the capital to look for information pertaining to Isei Province&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Rakan (Luohan)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Member of Ra Clan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Clan head&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Weirdo who wears monocles&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Maomao&amp;#8217;s father &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;dotes on her&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;totally against marrying her away to Jinshi &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(ARC5) actually yelled that out he won&amp;#8217;t ever give her away at the front doors of Rokushoukan &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;which sparks rumours&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Dumped a lot of useless work on Jinshi to keep him busy&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Prosopagnosia &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Can see Fenshen&amp;#8217;s and Maomao&amp;#8217;s face&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Close people look like Shogi pieces &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Jinshi &amp;#8211; Gold General&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Gaoshun &amp;#8211; Promoted Silver&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Ruomen &amp;#8211; Promoted Rook&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Chue &amp;#8211; Knight&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Young Rikuson (13 year old) &amp;#8211; Pawn &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Rikuson &amp;#8211; Promoted Pawn?&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Unknown people are Go stones&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Possesses eyes that can see the genuineness of people&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Specialty is Shogi and Go&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Loves gossip&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Can&amp;#8217;t Drink. At all.&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Tactician/strategist of the military&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Neutral Faction of the Imperial Court&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(End of LN2)&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt; Redeems Fenshen, LN only&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN6)&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt; Marries Fenshen, LN only&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC7) Hosts a Go tournament&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC8) Joined the expedition to the Western Capital &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;The Western Capital is looking forward to his presence&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC9) Was in Isei Province seventeen years ago before the purge of the Ih clan &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;played shogi in the shogi hall every day&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Met Rin-taijin and Rikuson there&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Rakan&amp;#8217;s father&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Mentioned ARC2, makes an appearance in ARC5&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(Ex)Member of Ra Clan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Previous clan head before getting driven out by Rakan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Used to be a high-ranking military official&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Relatively normal for a Ra Clan member&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Had a wife, whom he left for a concubine after Rakan was born&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Disappointed in both his sons&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Rakan&amp;#8217;s half-brother (Rakou; Luohong)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Mentioned in ARC2, makes an appearance in ARC5&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(Ex)Member of Ra Clan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Rakan&amp;#8217;s younger brother from another mother&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Relatively normal for a Ra Clan member&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Talented? in farming &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Grows sweet potatoes&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC 9) Correction. CRAZY about potatoes.&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Quite a schemer himself&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Still corresponds with his son through letters&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC 9) Sent to the Northern Province to see if the land can grow sweet potatoes&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Rahan&amp;#8217;s mother&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC5&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;An arranged marriage to Rakou &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Sides with Rakou&amp;#8217;s father&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;A beauty if it wasn&amp;#8217;t for her personality&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Tired of the country life&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Another zealous believer of Lady Pai&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Rahan&amp;#8217;s older brother&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC5&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(Ex)Member of Ra Clan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Relatively normal for a Ra Clan member &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;could go on to become a normal official if he cuts away from the family&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Inferiority complex towards his little brother&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC 9) Posted to the Western Capital as the farming expert in potatoes&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Well-versed in all things potatoes: farming and cooking&amp;#8230;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;A really good farmer &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;doesn&amp;#8217;t like to hear that&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;A good eldest brother, if he were in a normal good family&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Easily riled up&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Looks blunt spoken, but actually a softy&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC10 end) His name is Kan Junjie &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Renpuu (Lianfeng)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC3&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Rouran&amp;#8217;s maid&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Looks like Rouran?&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Rifa (Lihua)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Able Consort&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Sickly due to face powder &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;lead poisoning&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Good relationship with Maomao after she comes to heal her &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Maomao would back her if she wasn&amp;#8217;t with Gyokuyou&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Gave Maomao a kanzashi&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Melons&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Charismatic but too nice&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Her son the Crown Prince died at the beginning of the story&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Cousins with her head maid Shin&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC3 end) has another son&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Rihaku (Li bai)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Promotion stock&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Military officer &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;his ranking is high enough to do desk work, but it doesn&amp;#8217;t fit him&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;works under Rakan? &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;his office was close to the weirdo so he knows quite a lot of gossip&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;In the Imperial Guard?&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC5) Given an important post under Jinshi&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Maomao calls him Mongrel&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Strong &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Skilled with a six-sided club&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Nice guy&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Utterly infatuated with Pairin &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;willing to do whatever it takes to redeem Pairin himself&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;goes to the Rokushoukan every holiday to get a glimpse of her at least&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC8) Joined the expedition to the Western Capital &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;as the quack doctor&amp;#8217;s/Maomao&amp;#8217;s body guard&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Riishu (Lishu)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Virtuous Consort &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;still hasn&amp;#8217;t done with her duty as a consort&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Consort to Previous Emperor first&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Picky Eater &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Allergic to seafood&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;hates honey due to past mishap&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Timid&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Very close with Ah Duo &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;treats her like a mother&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;her mother was friends with Ah Duo and the emperor&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Bullied by her own maids&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC4) &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Rumours that she is the child of the U Clan lady and the emperor&lt;/span&gt; &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Jossed. Her father is Uryuu &amp;#8211; same fish allergy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC4)&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt; Bethrothed to Jinshi&lt;/span&gt; &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;(END OF ARC4) Crushing hard on Basen&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Called off&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(END of ARC5) Retired to religion&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Rikuson (Lusun)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Introduced in ARC4&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Rakan&amp;#8217;s subordinate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Gentle&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Slender&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Special skill &amp;#8211; can remember any face he sees once&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Diligent despite his appearance&lt;/span&gt; &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Gaoshun number 2&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC5) Part of the emperor&amp;#8217;s spy network? &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(ARC9) Ih clan male relative spy network?&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(Arc 7/LN8) Dispatched to the western capital as Gyoku&amp;#8217;ou&amp;#8217;s advisor &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Given odd jobs to work on&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(Arc 8) trying hard to look for ways to improve the food supply situation in the Western Capital&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC9) Knew about Nenjen and the ritual &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Apparently heard it from an acquaintance &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(END of ARC9) Knowledge taught by his mother and elder sister&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(END of ARC9) Survivor of the Ih Clan &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Son of the last family head&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Was planning to be a merchant when he left his family if it wasn&amp;#8217;t for the purge&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(END of ARC9) Met Rakan seventeen years ago in the shogi hall &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;called Teeny Pawn&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(END OF ARC9) Murdered Gyoku&amp;#8217;ou&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;RinRii (Lingli)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Imperial Princess&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Emperor and Gyokuyou&amp;#8217;s daughter&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Tomboy&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Can walk now&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC7/LN8) Can speak now&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Rin-taijin (Lin-daren)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC 9&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;An eighty year old elderly man from the western capital &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;senile&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;full body tremor&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;hunchbacked&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;carries a cane&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Inarticulate, but understandable when he says simple words&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Walking encyclopaedia of the western capital &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;meticulous and prudent in the past&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;used to compile historical texts about the western capital &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;attacked by a mob during the Ih clan purge seventeen years ago due to relation with said clan (not blood related so spared) &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;losing his lifework as a result when everything is burned&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;which probably caused his dementia&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Has a library &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;which got burnt down because of the mob&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;apparently has a hidden one which holds all the copies&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Shogi master &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;used to play games with Rakan in the past &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;old friend of Rakan &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;they played at the shogi hall&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Rakan recognises playstyle&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;regains clarity/sanity while playing&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Rin-shoujin (Lin-xiaoren)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC 9&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Middle-aged man from the western capital&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Rin-taijin&amp;#8217;s faithful caretaker&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Recording his grandfather&amp;#8217;s shogi matches &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;in a bid to learn where his hidden library is&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;NOT related to Rin-shoujin &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;actually monitoring him&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;ran away with something after they figured out where Rin-taijin&amp;#8217;s hidden stash was&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;At large&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC9 end) A part of Chue&amp;#8217;s spy network &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;worked together with her to secure the family register that was in Rin-taijin&amp;#8217;s hidden library&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Rokushoukan Owner (Okan-san)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Introduced in ARC4&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Rumoured to be the son of the previous owner and the Rokushoukan madam&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Owns another business that involves dealing with grain&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Hopeless person&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Henpecked husband?&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Rouran (Loulan)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Introduced ARC2&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Pure Consort after Ah Duo&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Member of the Shi Clan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Daughter of the Prime Minister Shishou&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Changes clothes a lot, looks like a different person each time&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Doll-like, no personality, does as her mother tells her&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Always disappears from her palace &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;leaving her maids to disguise as her&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Playing around as the maid Shisui &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;uses this time to catch bugs and gather medicinal herbs&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;and chat with Maomao and Shaoran&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Hated the idea of being a mother&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Schemed to have her older sister Suirei and the Shi Clan Children survive&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Left Jinshi information about future locust plague&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Scratched Jinshi&amp;#8217;s face&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN4) Equated to a Vixen&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Deceased &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(LN4) from getting shot in the chest and falling off the fortress&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(End of LN4) survives, assumes a new name &amp;#8220;&lt;a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tamamo-no-Mae"&gt;Tamamo&lt;/a&gt;&amp;#8221;  &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;last seen running towards the port for a ship that is bound for a certain island country&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Ruomen (Luomen)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Member of the Ra Clan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Maomao&amp;#8217;s adoptive father and great uncle&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Outstanding physician banished from the inner palace now working in the pleasure district &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;due to the death of Ah Duo&amp;#8217;s son&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC3) Back in the Inner Palace to aid with Gyokuyou&amp;#8217;s pregnancy &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(LN4) &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;To aid Gyokuyou for her breech birth &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;remains as Gyokuyou&amp;#8217;s personal physician&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Planted a lot of medicinal herbs in the Inner Palace&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Walks with one leg dragging&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC6) Stays in the medical office furthest away from the military side hahaha&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC8) Sequestered in the Inner Palace while the main crew goes to the Western Capital&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Sazen (Zuoshan)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;del&gt;terrified of poison maidens&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Introduced in ARC3&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;A worker in the Shi Clan fortress who escaped during the fire&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Named in ARC4 &amp;#8211; a new name so Chou&amp;#8217;u wouldn&amp;#8217;t recall him&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Handy &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Maomao has him take over the pharmacy whenever she goes out&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Manservant apprentice &amp;gt; pharmacist apprentice&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Shaoran (Xiaolan)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Maidservant of the Inner Palace&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Friends with Maomao&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Friendly and doesn&amp;#8217;t care much about ranking&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Child-like/innocent&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;A good source of Inner Palace Rumours&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Has a sweet tooth&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN3)&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt; Maomao taught her how to write&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN4)&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt; Found employment with a low-ranked consort&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;ARC5 &lt;span style="color: #333333"&gt;&amp;#8211; mentioned that she has gone out to look for work when her term in the inner palace ended&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Shenmei (Shenmei)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Member of the Shi Clan &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;daughter of the previous clan head&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Shishou&amp;#8217;s main wife &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Bethrothed from 20 years ago finally returned to him&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Rouran&amp;#8217;s mother&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Once a consort from the era of the Previous Emperor &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Entered court as the Empress had asked Shenmei&amp;#8217;s father &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;as a way to keep an eye on the clan&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Once a peerless beauty &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;went ugly in her age&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Came back with a thorn in her side and a venomous personality&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Jealousy-ridden &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;envious of those more beautiful than her &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;previous emperor and Jinshi&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Conspired to ruin the country for the grievance it gave her &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt; split the clan up, all the people who stood against her left and the ones who stayed were all good-for-nothings&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;fooled by her husband and daughter who played along with her&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Deceased from blood loss due to shrapnel embedded in her face from the misfire of new model hand cannon&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Shenryu (Shenlü)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;A middle-aged court lady who works in the clinic&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Practised with diagnosing people&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Reliable&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Mixed blooded, green eyes&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;One of the young girls touched by the Previous Emperor &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;unable to leave the inner palace until she dies&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Conspired with Rouran to kidnap Maomao from the Inner Palace&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Tried to commit suicide by biting off her tongue when pressured by Jinshi about Maomao&amp;#8217;s location&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC4) &lt;span style="color: #333333"&gt;mentioned that she is treated as a criminal but kept her life&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Shi Clan children&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Members of the Shi Clan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Five children&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;All of them drugged by Rouran to escape going up to the gallows&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;All woke up fine &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;except for one. See Chou&amp;#8217;u&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(End of ARC3) Four of them are taken under Ah Dou&amp;#8217;s wing&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Shin (Xing)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Rifa&amp;#8217;s head maid&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Rifa&amp;#8217;s cousin&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Petty and spiteful&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Thinks she is above Rifa, doesn&amp;#8217;t understand why she isn&amp;#8217;t the consort&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Graceful beauty&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;The daughter of the clan head&amp;#8217;s brother&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC3) Banished from the Inner Palace &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;tried to make an abortion drug for Rifa from perfumes&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;reason for all of Rifa&amp;#8217;s incompetent maids&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Shishou (Zichang)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Member of the Shi Clan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Clan head &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;branch member adopted into the main family&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Prime Minister&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Plump and cunning&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Called the Raccoon Geezer in the Imperial Court&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Highly favoured by the Empress &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;prompted her to increase the size of the inner palace &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;as a way to combat the slave trade&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Emperor is no match for him in influence &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;forced his daughter Rouran to the Pure Consort seat&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Secretly sheltered the Banished Princess and the former physician &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Married the Princess with the Previous Emperor&amp;#8217;s blessing when he succeeded as the next clan head&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Later married Shenmei, his betrothed from twenty years ago, who got returned to him after he got the trust of the empress and the previous emperor&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Has two daughters &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Shisui, from a town girl (See Suirei&amp;#8217;s mother)&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Rouran, from Shenmei&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Loyal to the country &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;played along with his wife who wanted to ruin the country &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;always planned to die so her plan would never go through&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Deceased &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ran down by three swords one after another&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Shisui (Inner Palace maid) (Zicui)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Maid that works under a consort&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Innocent&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Tall&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Shrill-voiced&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Loves insects&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;has an older sister who&amp;#8217;s good at medicine &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;who taught her how to make simple medicines&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Joins in with Maomao and Shaoran in their conversations&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;See Rouran&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Shisui (Real) (Zicui)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;See Suirei&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Sourin (Shuanglin)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC3&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Rouran&amp;#8217;s maid&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Looks like Rouran?&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Suirei (Cuiling)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Member of the Shi Clan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;An Imperial Court lady &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(LN2) &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;close to the imperial court physician on the military side&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN2) &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;allowed to tend a garden plot near the stables&lt;/span&gt; &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(LN2) &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;growing all kind of plants, even datura&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN2) &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;poisoned herself when several assassination incidents were linked to her &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN4) &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Enters the inner palace with the new intake of eunuchs&lt;/span&gt; &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(LN4) &lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;drags Rouran away from the Inner Palace&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN4)&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt; Compels Maomao to leave with her&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Tall&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Outstanding doctor&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Bullied by her stepmother&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Shishou&amp;#8217;s oldest daughter&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Compounded the resurrection drug that was fed to the Shi Clan kids&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(End of ARC3) The Previous Emperor&amp;#8217;s granddaughter &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;wears a phoenix on her&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(End of ARC3) Taken under Ah Duo&amp;#8217;s wing&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Suirei&amp;#8217;s mother&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Banished Princess&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;A town girl who is raised by her father(?) &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;&amp;#8220;Father&amp;#8221; is the physician who was blamed to have impregnated a young maid of a consort&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Sheltered by Shishou as a baby&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Taken in as Shishou&amp;#8217;s first wife when she grew up&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Murdered by Shenmei?&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Oldest child of the Previous Emperor &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Should&amp;#8217;ve been an Imperial Princess&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Suiren (Shuilian)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Jinshi&amp;#8217;s nanny&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Middle-aged&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Mean&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Capable &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt; does most work alone&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(Arc 8) Joins the expedition to the Western Capital &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;as one of Jinshi&amp;#8217;s attendants&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Taomei (Taomei)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Arc 8&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Gaoshun&amp;#8217;s wife&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Mother of Maamei, Baryou, and Basen&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Looks like an older version of Maamei&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Blind in one eye from injury&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Joins the expedition to the Western Capital &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;as one of Jinshi&amp;#8217;s attendants&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Tenyuu (Tianyou)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;(WN) Civil Official &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;LN counterpart is named Sei instead&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC6) hired by Jinshi as a substitute document sorter while Basen was recovering from his injuries&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC7) still employed&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Loves Go&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN) A young court physician &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;has the hots for En&amp;#8217;en?&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Stubborn&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Surgery skill best among the apprentice cohort&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Emotionally dull/not fazed by much&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(Arc 8) Joins the expedition the Western Capital &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;as an apprentice court physician&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Ukyou (Youjiao)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Introduced in ARC4&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Manservant head of the Rokushoukan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Been around long before Maomao was born&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Capable&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Married to a retired courtesan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Loves children &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;used to piggyback Maomao when she was younger&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;plays with Chou&amp;#8217;u and the kamuro&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC5) Part of the emperor&amp;#8217;s spy network? &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Mi clan? or former Ih clan?&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Uryuu (Maoliu)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Introduced in ARC4&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Head of the U Clan&lt;/span&gt; &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Riishu&amp;#8217;s father&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Adopted into the family as son-in-law&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;The second son of a wealthy merchant&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Middle-aged with a medium build&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Good business sense&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Short fuse&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Has a concubine&lt;/span&gt; &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;has a son and another daughter (See, (ARC5) Yakou)&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Tries to send his other daughter into the inner palace&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Seafood allergy&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Yaachin (Yaqin)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Mentioned ARC 9/ Introduced LN10&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Gyoku&amp;#8217;ou&amp;#8217;s adopted daughter&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Green eyed red haired foreign beauty&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Entered the inner palace as of ARC9/LN10&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Yakou (Yeguang)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC5&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;&amp;#8220;Died&amp;#8221; &lt;/span&gt; &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Apparently hung herself off the tower&lt;/span&gt; &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;the body fell into the pond and never found &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;a huge funeral was held for her&lt;/span&gt; &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;A plot thought up by Lady Pai to get her out of the estate&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Conspires with Lady Pai to get rid of her sister Consort Riishu&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;&lt;span style="color: #000000"&gt;Zealous believer of Lady Pai&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Yao (Yao)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;ARC6&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;A court lady &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;court physician assistant&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Master relationship with En&amp;#8217;en&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;A sheltered, wealthy young lady &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;her father passed away so her uncle took over the family&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;became a court lady to escape being a tool to be married off&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Supposed to have been the top scorer of the exam &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;can&amp;#8217;t see eye to eye with Maomao because of that&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Big chest&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Sixteen years old (through kazoe counting system)&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(END of ARC6) Due to getting mushroom poisoning from a botched food tasting job, her liver is damaged &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;refrain from sodium and alcohol&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Tsundere&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Dislikes eating strange things &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Loves eating Hasma even though she doesn&amp;#8217;t know what it is&amp;#8230;&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(Arc 8) Learning how to handle kitchen knives &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Set on becoming a court physician despite her misgivings towards dissecting human cadavers&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(ARC 9) Sends a letter to Maomao, asking about how she is &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;concealing a secret message when read with Rahan&amp;#8217;s letter&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;Zuurin (Zilin)&lt;/p&gt;    &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Introduced in ARC4&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Mute kamuro in the Rokushoukan&lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;Sticks very close to Chou&amp;#8217;u, who protects her from the other children &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;Chou&amp;#8217;u told her that he will redeem when they grow up. Aww&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt;    &lt;li&gt;(LN5) The sickly second daughter of a poor man who pawned both his daughters away to Rokushoukan for Maomao to treat her &lt;ul class="wp-block-list"&gt; &lt;li&gt;her older sister became a low class courtesan&lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt; &lt;/li&gt; &lt;/ul&gt;    &lt;p&gt;&lt;/p&gt; &lt;div id="jp-post-flair" class="sharedaddy sd-like-enabled"&gt;&lt;div class="sharedaddy sd-sharing-enabled"&gt;&lt;div class="robots-nocontent sd-block sd-social sd-social-official sd-sharing"&gt;&lt;h3 class="sd-title"&gt;Share this:&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;div class="sd-content"&gt;&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li class="share-facebook"&gt;&lt;div class="fb-share-button" data-href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/knh-characters/" data-layout="button_count"&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li class="share-end"&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ul&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class='sharedaddy sd-block sd-like jetpack-likes-widget-wrapper jetpack-likes-widget-unloaded' id='like-post-wrapper-130534757-2012-68ac7d8537bcb' data-src='//widgets.wp.com/likes/index.html?ver=20250825#blog_id=130534757&amp;amp;post_id=2012&amp;amp;origin=shikarito.wordpress.com&amp;amp;obj_id=130534757-2012-68ac7d8537bcb' data-name='like-post-frame-130534757-2012-68ac7d8537bcb' data-title='Like or Reblog'&gt;&lt;div class='likes-widget-placeholder post-likes-widget-placeholder' style='height: 55px;'&gt;&lt;span class='button'&gt;&lt;span&gt;Like&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span class='loading'&gt;Loading&amp;#8230;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;span class='sd-text-color'&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;a class='sd-link-color' href="https://shikarito.wordpress.com/kusuriya-no-hitorigoto/knh-characters/"&gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/main&gt;</description>
